text.tspan: Excess mortality: Deaths from all causes compared to average over
The percentage difference between the reported number of weekly or monthly deaths in 2020–2024 — broken down by age
group — and the average number of deaths in the same period over the years 2015–2019.
Data source: Human Mortality Database (2023); World Mortality Dataset (2023)
Note: The reported number of deaths might not count all deaths that occurred due to incomplete coverage and delays in reporting.
